snippet: Kristine Anigwe and Penina Davidson each had double-doubles, Courtney Range scored 17 points and No. 21 California beat Arizona 74-64 on Thursday night in the Pac-12 opener for both teams....
lead_paragraph: Kristine Anigwe and Penina Davidson each had double-doubles, Courtney Range scored 17 points and No. 21 California beat Arizona 74-64 on Thursday night in the Pac-12 opener for both teams.

headline.main: Anigwe, Davidson Lead No. 21 Cal Women Past Arizona, 74-64
